---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import km1 from '../../assets/service locations/kings mountain/kings mountain nc_1.jpeg';
import km2 from '../../assets/service locations/kings mountain/kings mountain nc_2.jpg';
import km3 from '../../assets/service locations/kings mountain/kings mountain nc_3.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Web Design & Local SEO in Kings Mountain, NC"
  description="Professional web design and local SEO for Kings Mountain, NC businesses. We build websites that connect your business with customers across Cleveland County and the surrounding communities."
>

  <section class="py-24 lg:py-40 px-4 relative bg-[#0A0A0A] overflow-hidden" data-animate>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-25">
      <Image src={km1} alt="Kings Mountain, NC business neighborhood" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0A0A0A] via-[#0A0A0A]/90 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_50%,rgba(0,180,216,0.18),transparent_55%)]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 rounded-full border border-brand-glow/30 bg-brand-glow/20 text-brand-glow text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm">
        ✦ Local Growth for Kings Mountain Businesses
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[0.9]">
        Kings Mountain Websites <br /><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Built for Local Leads.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We build websites and SEO campaigns that help Kings Mountain businesses attract customers from Shelby, Gastonia, and the surrounding communities. Local-first design, faster performance, and clear paths to contact.  
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="/contact"
          class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent-light transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(132,204,22,0.4)] overflow-hidden"
        >
          <span class="relative z-10">Schedule a Free Strategy Call</span>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 translate-x-[-100%] group-hover:translate-x-[0%] bg-white/20 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-brand-darkest border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-tight">
          Is Your Kings Mountain Business <span class="text-brand-cyan">Visible Where It Counts?</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-red-500">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70"><span class="text-white font-semibold">Hidden from local map searches?</span> If you aren’t ranking for Kings Mountain searches, nearby customers are choosing competitors before they even see your business.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-red-500">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70"><span class="text-white font-semibold">Your website feels out of date?</span> Modern customers expect fast-loading pages and clear calls to action—anything else loses clicks and trust.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-1 text-red-500">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70"><span class="text-white font-semibold">Too much competition from big agencies?</span> Local Kings Mountain businesses deserve a website partner who understands Cleveland County—not a distant team that treats you like a number.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <Image src={km2} alt="Kings Mountain storefront" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl aspect-square object-cover" />
        <Image src={km3} alt="Kings Mountain small business" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl aspect-square object-cover mt-8" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Kings Mountain Digital Growth <span class="text-brand-accent">Made Local.</span></h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
          We focus on Kings Mountain search behavior, neighborhood intent, and local landmarks so your site reaches customers at the exact moment they are ready to hire.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <Image src={km1} alt="Kings Mountain neighborhood" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-full shadow-lg" />
        <Image src={km2} alt="Kings Mountain business" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-full shadow-lg" />
        <Image src={km3} alt="Kings Mountain community" class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-full shadow-lg" />
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-brand-accent text-4xl font-black mb-2">Local</div>
          <div class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">Kings Mountain SEO</div>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm">We optimize your website and listings for the exact phrases Kings Mountain customers are using right now.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-brand-cyan text-4xl font-black mb-2">Modern</div>
          <div class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">Custom Web Design</div>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm">A polished website that loads fast, looks great on mobile, and converts visits into phone calls and inquiries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-brand-blue text-4xl font-black mb-2">Transparent</div>
          <div class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">Local Partnership</div>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm">We provide clear pricing, reliable support, and monthly reports so Kings Mountain business owners feel confident every step of the way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-brand-darkest">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="flex-1 order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <Image src={km3} alt="Kings Mountain storefront" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl aspect-[3/4] object-cover" />
          <Image src={km2} alt="Kings Mountain local marketing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl aspect-[3/4] object-cover mt-12" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 order-1 lg:order-2">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Websites That Convert Kings Mountain Traffic.</h2>
        <div class="space-y-10">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Speak Directly to Local Customers</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 leading-relaxed">From shoppers on York Road to residents near the battlefield park, your website should feel familiar, professional, and easy to act on.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Make Search Engines Understand You</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 leading-relaxed">We build content and technical SEO that tells Google exactly where you operate and which services you offer best in Kings Mountain.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Keep the Momentum Going</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 leading-relaxed">Your website is only the start. We support ongoing updates, local SEO, and site care so your web presence keeps working as your business grows.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-4 relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-accent/90" data-animate>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 text-[#0A0A0A]">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
        Ready to Grow Your Kings Mountain Business Online?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium mb-10 opacity-90 text-balance">
        If you're ready for a website that attracts customers in Cleveland County and beyond, let's build it together.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-black text-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl"
        >
          Book a Free Chat
        </a>
        <a 
          href="tel:+17044738188"
          class="inline-block border-2 border-[#0A0A0A] text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-black text-xl hover:bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:text-white transition-all duration-300"
        >
          (704) 473-8188
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
